<div class="detail">

 <span><p><strong>Tracking in your account (Highly Recommended ):</strong><br>
 Login your account to track your orders. Create a account with which allows you to shop faster, 
 track the status of your current orders, review your previous orders and take advantage of our other member's benefits.</p>
 <p>If you have any questions about your orders, please <a href="/uc/helpCenter/help1-7" >Leave us a Message</a> with your account in our store, Joybuy will reply you in 8hrs.</p><br></span>
 <span><p><strong>By email (Recommended ):</strong><br> We are always happy to hear from our customers. You can contact us via e-mail <a href="mailto:service@joybuy.co.uk">service@joybuy.co.uk </a>
<a href="mailto:sales@joybuy.co.uk">sales@joybuy.co.uk</a>.</p></span>
<span><p><strong>By Phone:</strong><br>You can call us 86-592-5183012 for your order progress, do remember your order number. It is not easy for us to check your order status without your order number.</p></span>
<span><p><strong>Default Process:</strong><br>Once you placed the order, we may ship your item in 2 working days for the in stock item. 
  And for the custom made item, we may ship your item in 15-20 working days.And usually by DHL it takes 3-5 working days for shipping to your door. Please see more about Shipping & Delivery in <a href="/uc/helpCenter/more-2">Part2.</a></p><br></span>
